metadata.name: Prime № 1 - Indefinite Parcel
metadata.description:
“Indefinite Parcels” is a generative art collection. The art explores how a viewer can experience art from different distances. Large, dominate elements are mixed with very small details to create a very dynamic and multi-layered piece of art. The viewer can immerse themselves into each piece both at a distance and up close. 


https://www.cryptobauhaus.com/nftcollections/indefinite-parcel
